Documentation.name: Geodata Tools
Documentation.notes: Contains scripts ands model searches to support data modelling according to the Danish Basic Data modelling rules, developed at the Danish Geodata Agency. Note that the URL mentioned for this MDG Technology is only accessible from within the Danish Geodata Agency.

RootTable.Filter: select c.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, c.Connector_Type as CLASSTYPE, o_start.Name as "Name Start", c.Name as "Name Assocation", c.DestRole, o_end.Name as "Name End" from (t_connector c inner join t_object o_start on c.Start_Object_ID = o_start.Object_ID) inner join t_object o_end on c.End_Object_ID = o_end.Object_ID where o_start.Package_ID in (#Branch#) and c.Connector_Type in ('Association' , 'Aggregation') and c.Direction in ('Source -> Destination', 'Bi-Directional') and c.DestRole is null union all select c.ea_guid, c.Connector_Type, o_end.Name, c.Name, c.SourceRole, o_start.Name from (t_connector c inner join t_object o_start on c.Start_Object_ID = o_start.Object_ID) inner join t_object o_end on c.End_Object_ID = o_end.Object_ID where o_end.Package_ID in (#Branch#) and c.Connector_Type in ('Association' , 'Aggregation') and c.Direction in ('Destination -> Source', 'Bi-Directional') and c.SourceRole is null ;

select c.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, c.Connector_Type as CLASSTYPE, o_start.Name as "Name Start", c.Name as "Name Assocation", o_end.Name as "Name End" from (t_connector c inner join t_object o_start on c.Start_Object_ID = o_start.Object_ID) inner join t_object o_end on c.End_Object_ID = o_end.Object_ID where o_start.Package_ID in (#Branch#) and c.Connector_Type in ('Association', 'Aggregation') and c.Direction in ('Source -> Destination', 'Bi-Directional') and o_end.Stereotype like '*objekttype' and (not exists (select * from t_taggedvalue tv where tv.ElementID = c.ea_guid and tv.BaseClass = 'ASSOCIATION_TARGET' and tv.TagValue = 'inlineOrByReference') or (select CStr(Notes) from t_taggedvalue tv where tv.ElementID = c.ea_guid and tv.BaseClass = 'ASSOCIATION_TARGET' and tv.TagValue = 'inlineOrByReference') <> 'inline') union all select c.ea_guid, c.Connector_Type, o_end.Name, c.Name, o_start.Name from (t_connector c inner join t_object o_start on c.Start_Object_ID = o_start.Object_ID) inner join t_object o_end on c.End_Object_ID = o_end.Object_ID where o_end.Package_ID in (#Branch#) and c.Connector_Type in ('Association', 'Aggregation') and c.Direction in ('Destination -> Source', 'Bi-Directional') and o_start.Stereotype like '*objekttype' and (not exists (select * from t_taggedvalue tv where tv.ElementID = c.ea_guid and tv.BaseClass = 'ASSOCIATION_SOURCE' and tv.TagValue = 'inlineOrByReference') or (select CStr(Notes) from t_taggedvalue tv where tv.ElementID = c.ea_guid and tv.BaseClass = 'ASSOCIATION_SOURCE' and tv.TagValue = 'inlineOrByReference') <> 'inline') #DB=# The second part of the union may find elements that have to be corrected in another package, see EA help Add Connectors To Locked Elements #DB=#

select a.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, 'Attribute' as CLASSTYPE, o.name, a.name, a.scope from t_attribute a inner join t_object o on a.object_id = o.object_id where o.package_id in (#Branch#) and a.Scope <> 'Public' order by o.name, a.name

select a.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, 'Attribute' as CLASSTYPE, o.Name as Object_Name, '' as Assocation_Name, a.Name as Property_Name, '' as Association_End from t_attribute a inner join t_object o on a.Object_ID = o.Object_ID where o.Package_ID in (#Branch#) and a.UpperBound = '*' and not exists (select * from t_attributetag at where at.ElementID = a.ID and at.Property = 'maxOccurs') union all select c.ea_guid, c.Connector_Type, o_start.Name, c.Name, c.DestRole, o_end.Name from (t_connector c inner join t_object o_start on c.Start_Object_ID = o_start.Object_ID) inner join t_object o_end on c.End_Object_ID = o_end.Object_ID where o_start.Package_ID in (#Branch#) and Right(c.DestCard, 1) = '*' and c.Connector_Type in ('Association' , 'Aggregation') and c.Direction in ('Source -> Destination', 'Bi-Directional') and not exists (select * from t_taggedvalue tv where tv.ElementID = c.ea_guid and tv.BaseClass = 'ASSOCIATION_TARGET' and tv.TagValue = 'maxOccurs') union all select c.ea_guid, c.Connector_Type, o_end.Name, c.Name, c.SourceRole, o_start.Name from (t_connector c inner join t_object o_start on c.Start_Object_ID = o_start.Object_ID) inner join t_object o_end on c.End_Object_ID = o_end.Object_ID where o_end.Package_ID in (#Branch#) and Right(c.SourceCard, 1) = '*' and c.Connector_Type in ('Association' , 'Aggregation') and c.Direction in ('Destination -> Source', 'Bi-Directional') and not exists (select * from t_taggedvalue tv where tv.ElementID = c.ea_guid and tv.BaseClass = 'ASSOCIATION_SOURCE' and tv.TagValue = 'maxOccurs') order by 1, 3;

SELECT t_attribute.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, 'Attribute' as CLASSTYPE, t_package.Name as PackageName, t_object.Name AS ClassName, t_attribute.Name AS AttributeName FROM ((t_attribute INNER JOIN t_object ON t_object.Object_ID = t_attribute.Object_ID) INNER JOIN t_package ON t_package.Package_ID = t_object.Package_ID) WHERE t_object.Package_ID IN (#Branch#) AND t_object.Object_Type IN ('Class','Enumeration') AND (t_attribute.Name LIKE '* *' OR StrComp(Left(t_attribute.Name,1),UCase(Left(t_attribute.Name,1)),0) = 0) ORDER BY t_package.Name, t_object.Name, t_attribute.Name

select c.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, c.Connector_Type as CLASSTYPE, o_start.Name as "Name Start", c.Name as "Name Assocation", o_end.Name as "Name End" from (t_connector c inner join t_object o_start on c.Start_Object_ID = o_start.Object_ID) inner join t_object o_end on c.End_Object_ID = o_end.Object_ID where o_start.Package_ID in (#Branch#) and c.Connector_Type in ('Association', 'Aggregation') and c.Direction in ('Source -> Destination', 'Bi-Directional') and o_end.object_type = 'Class' and (not exists (select * from t_taggedvalue tv where tv.ElementID = c.ea_guid and tv.BaseClass = 'ASSOCIATION_TARGET' and tv.TagValue = 'inlineOrByReference') or (select CStr(Notes) from t_taggedvalue tv where tv.ElementID = c.ea_guid and tv.BaseClass = 'ASSOCIATION_TARGET' and tv.TagValue = 'inlineOrByReference') <> 'byReference') union all select c.ea_guid, c.Connector_Type, o_end.Name, c.Name, o_start.Name from (t_connector c inner join t_object o_start on c.Start_Object_ID = o_start.Object_ID) inner join t_object o_end on c.End_Object_ID = o_end.Object_ID where o_end.Package_ID in (#Branch#) and c.Connector_Type in ('Association', 'Aggregation') and c.Direction in ('Destination -> Source', 'Bi-Directional') and o_start.object_type = 'Class' and (not exists (select * from t_taggedvalue tv where tv.ElementID = c.ea_guid and tv.BaseClass = 'ASSOCIATION_SOURCE' and tv.TagValue = 'inlineOrByReference') or (select CStr(Notes) from t_taggedvalue tv where tv.ElementID = c.ea_guid and tv.BaseClass = 'ASSOCIATION_SOURCE' and tv.TagValue = 'inlineOrByReference') <> 'byReference') #DB=# The second part of the union may find elements that have to be corrected in another package, see EA help Add Connectors To Locked Elements #DB=# ;

select o.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, o.Object_Type as CLASSTYPE, o.* from t_object o where o.Package_ID in (#Branch#) and object_type in ('Class', 'Enumeration', 'DataType') and exists (select * from t_object o2 where o2.Package_ID in (#Branch#) and o2.Name = o.Name and o2.object_type = o.object_type and o2.ea_guid <> o.ea_guid);

select a.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, 'Attribute' as CLASSTYPE, o.Name as Object_Name, '' as Assocation_Name, a.Name as Property_Name, '' as Association_End from t_attribute a inner join t_object o on a.Object_ID = o.Object_ID where o.Package_ID in (#Branch#) and a.UpperBound <> '*' and exists (select * from t_attributetag at where at.ElementID = a.ID and at.Property = 'maxOccurs') union all select c.ea_guid, c.Connector_Type, o_start.Name, c.Name, c.DestRole, o_end.Name from (t_connector c inner join t_object o_start on c.Start_Object_ID = o_start.Object_ID) inner join t_object o_end on c.End_Object_ID = o_end.Object_ID where o_start.Package_ID in (#Branch#) and Right(c.DestCard, 1) <> '*' and c.Connector_Type in ('Association' , 'Aggregation') and c.Direction in ('Source -> Destination', 'Bi-Directional') and exists (select * from t_taggedvalue tv where tv.ElementID = c.ea_guid and tv.BaseClass = 'ASSOCIATION_TARGET' and tv.TagValue = 'maxOccurs') union all select c.ea_guid, c.Connector_Type, o_end.Name, c.Name, c.SourceRole, o_start.Name from (t_connector c inner join t_object o_start on c.Start_Object_ID = o_start.Object_ID) inner join t_object o_end on c.End_Object_ID = o_end.Object_ID where o_end.Package_ID in (#Branch#) and Right(c.SourceCard, 1) <> '*' and c.Connector_Type in ('Association' , 'Aggregation') and c.Direction in ('Destination -> Source', 'Bi-Directional') and exists (select * from t_taggedvalue tv where tv.ElementID = c.ea_guid and tv.BaseClass = 'ASSOCIATION_SOURCE' and tv.TagValue = 'maxOccurs') order by 1, 3;

select a.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, 'Attribute' as CLASSTYPE, o.name, a.name, at.property, at.value from (t_attribute a inner join t_object o on a.object_id = o.object_id) inner join t_attributetag at on a.id = at.elementid where o.package_id in (#Branch#) and property = 'definition' and (value is null or len(trim(value)) = 0) order by o.name, a.name

SELECT c.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, c.Connector_Type AS CLASSTYPE, c.Name, mid(c.StyleEx, 7, len(c.StyleEx) - 7) AS alias, o_src.name, c.SourceRole, c.SourceCard, o_target.name, c.DestRole, c.DestCard FROM (t_connector c inner join t_object o_src on c.start_object_id = o_src.object_id) inner join t_object o_target on c.end_object_id = o_target.object_id WHERE ((o_src.package_id in (#Branch#) and o_target.package_id in (#Branch#) and c.connector_type in ('Association', 'Aggregation')) or (o_src.package_id in (#Branch#) and (c.connector_type = 'Association' or (c.connector_type = 'Aggregation' and c.subtype = 'Weak'))) or (o_target.package_id in (#Branch#) and c.connector_type = 'Aggregation' and c.subtype = 'Strong')) and (c.SourceCard IS NULL or c.DestCard IS NULL) ORDER BY c.Name

select t_object.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, t_object.Object_Type as CLASSTYPE, t_object.* from t_object where t_object.Package_ID IN (#Branch#) and t_object.Object_Type <> 'Note' and not exists (select * from t_diagramobjects inner join t_diagram on t_diagramobjects.Diagram_ID = t_diagram.Diagram_ID where t_diagram.Package_ID IN (#Branch#) and t_diagramobjects.Object_ID = t_object.Object_ID);

#DB=# Should probably be updated at some point if it turns out that certain tagged values can be empty (e.g. because part of MDG) #DB=# select o.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, o.object_type as CLASSTYPE, o.Name as Object_Name, 'N/A' as Property_Name, op.property as Emtpy_Tagged_Value from t_object o inner join t_objectproperties op on o.object_id = op.object_id where o.Package_ID in (#Branch#) and (op.value is null or len(trim(op.value)) = 0); union all select a.ea_guid, 'Attribute', o.Name, a.Name, at.property from (t_attribute a inner join t_object o on a.Object_ID = o.Object_ID) inner join t_attributetag at on at.ElementID = a.ID where o.Package_ID in (#Branch#) and (at.value is null or len(trim(at.value)) = 0) union all select c.ea_guid, c.connector_type, c.Name, c.SourceRole, tv.tagvalue from (t_connector c inner join t_object o on c.Start_Object_ID = o.Object_ID) inner join t_taggedvalue tv on c.ea_guid = tv.elementid where o.Package_ID in (#Branch#) and Len(Trim(iif(tv.Notes is null, '', CStr(tv.Notes)))) = 0 union all select c.ea_guid, c.connector_type, c.Name, c.SourceRole, tv.tagvalue from (t_connector c inner join t_object o on c.End_Object_ID = o.Object_ID) inner join t_taggedvalue tv on c.ea_guid = tv.elementid where o.Package_ID in (#Branch#) and Len(Trim(iif(tv.Notes is null, '', CStr(tv.Notes)))) = 0

select o.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, o.object_type as CLASSTYPE, o.Name, o.object_type, o.gentype from t_object o where o.package_id in (#Branch#) and o.object_type in ('Class', 'DataType', 'Enumeration', 'Package') and (o.gentype is null or o.gentype <> '<none>')

SELECT c.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, c.Connector_Type AS CLASSTYPE, c.Name, mid(c.StyleEx, 7, len(c.StyleEx) - 7) AS alias, c.direction, o_src.name, c.SourceRole, o_target.name, c.DestRole, c.DestCard FROM (t_connector c inner join t_object o_src on c.start_object_id = o_src.object_id) inner join t_object o_target on c.end_object_id = o_target.object_id WHERE ((o_src.package_id in (#Branch#) and o_target.package_id in (#Branch#) and c.connector_type in ('Association', 'Aggregation')) or (o_src.package_id in (#Branch#) and (c.connector_type = 'Association' or (c.connector_type = 'Aggregation' and c.subtype = 'Weak'))) or (o_target.package_id in (#Branch#) and c.connector_type = 'Aggregation' and c.subtype = 'Strong')) and c.Direction = 'Unspecified' ORDER BY c.Name #DB=# do not use columns SourceIsNavigable and DestIsNavigable, the contents does often not match the model, use Direction instead #DB=#

SELECT t_package.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, 'Package' as CLASSTYPE, t_package.Name FROM t_package WHERE t_package.Package_ID IN (#Branch#) and (t_package.Name LIKE '* *' OR StrComp(Left(t_package.Name,1),UCase(Left(t_package.Name,1)),0) = 1) ORDER BY t_package.Name

select c.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, c.connector_type as CLASSTYPE, c.name, mid(c.StyleEx, 7, len(c.StyleEx) - 7) AS alias, o_src.name, c.SourceRole, o_target.name, c.DestRole from (t_connector c inner join t_object o_src on c.start_object_id = o_src.object_id) inner join t_object o_target on c.end_object_id = o_target.object_id where ((o_src.package_id in (#Branch#) and o_target.package_id in (#Branch#) and c.connector_type in ('Association', 'Aggregation')) or (o_src.package_id in (#Branch#) and (c.connector_type = 'Association' or (c.connector_type = 'Aggregation' and c.subtype = 'Weak'))) or (o_target.package_id in (#Branch#) and c.connector_type = 'Aggregation' and c.subtype = 'Strong') ) and c.name is null or len(trim(c.name)) = 0
select o.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, o.object_type as CLASSTYPE, o.name, o.scope from t_object o where o.package_id in (#Branch#) and o.scope <> 'Public' order by o.name

select o.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, o.object_type as CLASSTYPE, o.name, op.property, op.value from t_object o left join t_objectproperties op on o.object_id = op.object_id where o.package_id in (#Branch#) and property = 'definition' and (value is null or len(trim(value)) = 0) order by o.name

SELECT t_attribute.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, 'Attribute' as CLASSTYPE, t_package.Name as PackageName, t_object.Name AS ClassName, t_attribute.Name AS AttributeName, t_attribute.Type, t_attribute.Classifier FROM ((t_attribute INNER JOIN t_object ON t_object.Object_ID = t_attribute.Object_ID) INNER JOIN t_package ON t_package.Package_ID = t_object.Package_ID) WHERE t_object.Package_ID IN (#Branch#) AND t_object.Object_Type in ('Class', 'DataType') AND (t_attribute.Classifier = NULL OR t_attribute.Classifier = '0') ORDER BY t_package.Name, t_object.Name

select c.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, c.Connector_Type as CLASSTYPE, o_start.Name as "Name Start", c.Name as "Name Assocation", o_end.Name as "Name End", c.* from (t_connector c inner join t_object o_start on c.Start_Object_ID = o_start.Object_ID) inner join t_object o_end on c.End_Object_ID = o_end.Object_ID where (o_start.Package_ID in (#Branch#) or o_end.Package_ID in (#Branch#)) and c.Connector_Type = 'Aggregation' and ((c.DestIsAggregate <> 0 and c.Direction in ('Unspecified', 'Source -> Destination')) or (c.SourceIsAggregate <> 0 and c.Direction in ('Unspecified', 'Destination -> Source')))

select o.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, o.object_type as CLASSTYPE, o.name, op.property, op.value from (t_objectproperties op inner join t_object o on op.object_id = o.object_id) inner join t_package p on p.ea_guid = o.ea_guid where p.package_id in (#Branch#) and o.object_type in ('Package') and op.property not in ('forvaltingsopgave', 'modeldomæne', 'registermyndighed', 'status', 'version') #DB=typo i forvaltingsopgave, der mangler en n, men det er defineret sådan i grunddata-MDGen##DB=# union all select o.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, o.object_type as CLASSTYPE, o.name, op.property, op.value from t_objectproperties op inner join t_object o on op.object_id = o.object_id where o.package_id in (#Branch#) and o.object_type in ('Class', 'DataType', 'Enumeration') and op.property not in ('oracleName', 'profiles', 'transliteratedName','definition','note','eksempel','lovgrundlag','alternativtNavn') union all select a.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, 'Attribute' as CLASSTYPE, a.name, at.property, at.value from (t_attributetag at inner join t_attribute a on at.elementid = a.id) inner join t_object o on a.object_id = o.object_id where o.package_id in (#Branch#) and at.property not in ('maxOccurs', 'sequenceNumber', 'oracleName', 'profiles', 'size', 'transliteratedName','definition','note','eksempel','lovgrundlag','alternativtNavn') union all select c.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, c.connector_type as CLASSTYPE, c.name, tv.tagvalue, iif([tv].[Notes] IS NULL, '', [tv].[Notes]) from ((t_connector c inner join t_object o_start on c.start_object_id = o_start.object_id) inner join t_object o_end on c.end_object_id = o_end.object_id) inner join t_taggedvalue tv on tv.elementid = c.ea_guid where ((o_start.package_id in (#Branch#) and o_end.package_id in (#Branch#) and c.connector_type in ('Association', 'Aggregation')) or (o_start.package_id in (#Branch#) and (c.connector_type = 'Association' or (c.connector_type = 'Aggregation' and c.subtype = 'Weak'))) or (o_end.package_id in (#Branch#) and c.connector_type = 'Aggregation' and c.subtype = 'Strong')) and tv.tagvalue not in ('byReference', 'inline', 'inlineOrByReference', 'maxOccurs', 'sequenceNumber', 'oracleName', 'profiles', 'size', 'transliteratedName','definition','note','eksempel','lovgrundlag','alternativtNavn') order by 3

select d.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, d.Diagram_Type as CLASSTYPE, d.Name from t_diagram d where d.Package_ID IN (#Branch#) and not exists (select * from t_diagramobjects do inner join t_object o on o.Object_ID = do.Object_ID where do.Diagram_ID = d.Diagram_ID and o.NType = 18)

SELECT c.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, c.Connector_Type as CLASSTYPE, c.name, mid(c.StyleEx, 7, len(c.StyleEx) - 7) AS alias, o_src.name, c.SourceRole, c.Top_Start_Label, o_target.name, c.DestRole, c.Top_End_Label FROM (t_connector c inner join t_object o_src on c.start_object_id = o_src.object_id) inner join t_object o_target on c.end_object_id = o_target.object_id where ((o_src.package_id in (#Branch#) and o_target.package_id in (#Branch#) and c.connector_type in ('Association', 'Aggregation')) or (o_src.package_id in (#Branch#) and (c.connector_type = 'Association' or (c.connector_type = 'Aggregation' and c.subtype = 'Weak'))) or (o_target.package_id in (#Branch#) and c.connector_type = 'Aggregation' and c.subtype = 'Strong')) AND (c.SourceRole = NULL OR c.DestRole = NULL) ORDER BY c.Name

select c.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, c.connector_type as CLASSTYPE, c.name, mid(c.StyleEx, 7, len(c.StyleEx) - 7) AS alias, o_src.name, c.SourceRole, o_target.name, c.DestRole, tv.baseclass, tv.tagvalue, tv.notes from ((t_connector c inner join t_object o_src on c.start_object_id = o_src.object_id) inner join t_object o_target on c.end_object_id = o_target.object_id) inner join t_taggedvalue tv on tv.elementid = c.ea_guid where ((o_src.package_id in (#Branch#) and o_target.package_id in (#Branch#) and c.connector_type in ('Association', 'Aggregation')) or (o_src.package_id in (#Branch#) and (c.connector_type = 'Association' or (c.connector_type = 'Aggregation' and c.subtype = 'Weak'))) or (o_target.package_id in (#Branch#) and c.connector_type = 'Aggregation' and c.subtype = 'Strong') ) and tv.tagvalue = 'definition' and len(trim(left(iif(tv.notes is null, "", cstr(tv.notes)), iif(instr(1, iif(tv.notes is null, "", cstr(tv.notes)), '$ea_notes') = 0, len(iif(tv.notes is null, "", cstr(tv.notes))) + 1, instr(1, iif(tv.notes is null, "", cstr(tv.notes)), '$ea_notes')) - 1))) = 0 #DB=# The where value could probably be written simpler. Thinks to take into consideration: presence or absence of $ea_notes, and the fact that blank, non-empty definitions should also be traced #DB=#

SELECT t_object.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, t_object.Object_Type as CLASSTYPE, t_package.Name AS PackageName, t_object.Name AS ObjectName FROM t_object INNER JOIN t_package ON t_object.Package_ID = t_package.Package_ID WHERE t_object.Package_ID IN (#Branch#) AND Object_Type in ('Class', 'DataType', 'Enumeration') AND (t_object.Name LIKE '* *' OR StrComp(Left(t_object.Name,1),UCase(Left(t_object.Name,1)),0) = 1) ORDER BY t_package.Name, t_object.Name
select p.name, p.xmlpath from t_package p inner join t_object o on p.ea_guid = o.ea_guid where o.Package_ID in (#Branch#) and Instr(p.xmlpath, p.name & '.xml') = 0

Script.name: VAL Run and evaluate model validation searches
INFO Show sequenceNumber tagged value on properties of elements
CHG Use alias on all diagrams in package
CHG Set version, author and state on package, elements and diagram
INFO Show full path EA project
CHG Move documentation from Notes to tagged values
CHG Change all attributes to public scope
CHG Make attributes on enumerations literals
CHG Add tagged value inlineOrByReference with value byReference on compositions
CHG Add sequenceNumber tagged value on properties of elements
VAL Validate property names and roles
CHG Set scale to 100 on all diagrams in package
CHG Link the type on attributes to a type in the model
CHG Add tagged value inlineOrByReference with value byReference on associations
